graph TB
    subgraph "Llama Stack K8s Operator"
        Controller[Operator Controller Manager<br/>Deployment]
        LLSDController[LlamaStackDistribution Controller<br/>Watches CRDs]
        KustomizeEngine[Kustomize-based Deployment Engine<br/>Manifest Generation]
        FeatureFlags[Feature Flags Manager<br/>ConfigMap]
        ImageMapper[Distribution Image Mapper<br/>ConfigMap]
        NetworkTransformer[Network Policy Transformer<br/>Plugin]

        Controller -->|manages| LLSDController
        LLSDController -->|uses| KustomizeEngine
        LLSDController -->|reads config| FeatureFlags
        LLSDController -->|maps images| ImageMapper
        KustomizeEngine -->|generates policies| NetworkTransformer
    end

    User[User] -->|creates| LLSDCR[LlamaStackDistribution CR]
    LLSDCR -->|watched by| LLSDController

    subgraph "Created Resources"
        Deployment[Deployment<br/>Llama Stack Server]
        Service[Service<br/>ClusterIP 8321/TCP]
        PVC[PersistentVolumeClaim<br/>Model Storage]
        NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Optional]
        Ingress[Ingress<br/>Optional External Access]
    end

    LLSDController -->|creates| Deployment
    LLSDController -->|creates| Service
    LLSDController -->|creates| PVC
    LLSDController -->|creates| NetworkPolicy
    LLSDController -->|creates| Ingress

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>6443/TCP]
        ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime v0.19.4]
        KustomizeLib[kustomize kyaml v0.18.1]
        InferenceProvider[Inference Provider<br/>Ollama/vLLM/TGI]
    end

    Controller -->|depends on| ControllerRuntime
    KustomizeEngine -->|depends on| KustomizeLib
    Controller -->|reconciles via| K8sAPI
    Deployment -->|runs| InferenceProvider

    subgraph "Internal ODH/RHOAI Integrations"
        PrometheusOp[OpenShift Monitoring<br/>ServiceMonitor]
        SCC[Security Context Constraints<br/>anyuid]
    end

    Controller -.->|metrics| PrometheusOp
    Deployment -.->|requires| SCC

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px
    style LLSDController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style LLSDCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style K8sAPI fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ControllerRuntime fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style KustomizeLib fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style InferenceProvider fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style PrometheusOp fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style SCC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Deployment fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
    style Service fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
    style PVC fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
